Use inheritance to create an exception superclass (ExceptionA) and exception
subclasses ExceptionB and ExceptionC, where ExceptionB inherits from ExceptionA
and ExceptionC inherits from ExceptionB.

Write a program to demonstrate that the catch block for type ExcecptionA
catches exceptions of type ExceptionB and ExceptionC.

ExceptionA
    |
    V
ExceptionB
    |
    V
ExceptionC

